    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Sinopanorpa tincta (Navas). A–E. Male: A. Male adult, dorsal view; B. Abdomen of male with genital bulb, lateral view; C. Genital bulb, dorsal view; D. Genital bulb with hypovalves, ventral view; E. Genital bulb with hypovalves removed, ventral view. F–I. Female: F. Female adult, dorsal view; G. Subgenital plate, ventral view; H. Internal skeleton, ventral view; I. same, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5231065/files/figure.png" ;
